{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un efmnu preeſch ſaweem\nYaudim preeſch Ysraēlu weenu\nWeetu lizzis/ un tohs debſtijs/\nka tee ſawa Weeta dſihwo/ un\nwairs ne tohp ſchaubiti/ un beſ-\ndeewigi Yaudis tohs wairs ne\ndraggaſs/ libſs ka zittkahrt/"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un no tahs Deenas/ kad\neſ pawehlejn Sobgeem buht pahr\nmanneem Ysraēta Landim. Un\ntew eſimu eſ Duffſchann dewis\nno wiſſeim taweem Eenatdnee-\nkeem/ tas KUNGS arri tew\nStirnu dohd/ ka tas KUNGS\ntew grib weentu Namnu darriht."
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Rad taws Laiks buhs pa-\ngahjs/ un tu ar taweem Teh-\nweem afsmigſi/ tad uszelfchu eſ\ntawut Dſimmumu pehz tewis/\nkaſ no tawahm Mieefahmi nahks/\ntami apſtiprinaſchu eſ ſawu Wal-\nſtibu."
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas uſtaifibs mannam\nWahrdam weenu Naimnu/ un\neſ apſtiprinaſchu wiſa Walſti-\nbtu muhſchigt."
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es buhſchu wiſnam par\nTehwu/ un tas buhs man par\nDehlu/ kad tas ko taunu darra/\ntad eſ ar weenu zilwezigu Riht-\nſti wiſanu pahrimahzischu/ un ar\nZilweka Behrnu Sohdibahin."
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet manau Schehlaſtibu\nes no wiſa ne atrautchu/ itt ka"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet taws Namſ un t\nwa Walſtiba buhs pastahwig\ntawi Preeſchā muhſchigi: Tan\nFohda-Krehſlis buhs pastahwig\nmuhſchigi."
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Nahtans runnaja t\nus Dahwidu pehz wiſſeem tee\nWahrdcem/ un pehz wiſtu ſc\nParahdiſchanu."
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad nahze tas Kehninſ\nDahwids/ un palikſe preeſch\nKUNGA/ un fazzija: Kaſ eſi\nes Kungs/ KUNGS? un kaſi\nmans Namſ/ ka tu mann lih\nſchetjen waddijs eſi?"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tatschu tas wehl i\nmascekſch tawahmAzziin Kung\nKUNGS/ bet tu eſi arri t\nTawa Kalpa Nammu runna\nno nahkoſcheem ilgeem Laikeen\nſcht irr ta Wihe ta Zilweka/\nDeewa KUNGA."
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ko nu Dahwids wairs t\ntew runnahs/ jo tu paſihſti tan\nKalpu Kungs/ KUNGS."
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tawa Wahrdā labbad\nun pehz tawas Sirde eſi tu wi\nfas ſchahs leelas Leetas darrije\ntawam Kalpam tahs ſinnam\ndarridams."
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tapehz eſi tu augſte\nKUNGS Deews. Jo ne wee\nirr tahds ka tu/ un ne wee\nDeews irr ka tu ween/ pehz w\nu/ ko mehs ar muhſahmi Auft\naffam dſrdejſcht."
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kaſ irr ka tawi Ga\ndis/ ka Ysraēls? weena weent"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
